fields.title: Sue somebody
fields.dialog: [["Stan", "Kyle", "Lawyer"], [0, "We keep trying to tell him maybe this all isn't his fault."], [0, "Maybe the people who made the toilet are to blame for what happened."], [1, "So we were just wondering..."], [1, "if we could sue somebody."], [2, "You can always sue somebody."], [1, "All right, you see, Clyde."], [1, "Okay, we wanna help him sue whoever invented the toilet."], [2, "You got it."]]

fields.dialog: [["Officer 1", "Officer 2", "Randy", "Officer 3"], [0, "Put your coffee in the plastic tray, please, sir."], [1, "Shoes off. Belts off."], [2, "Yeah, yeah."], [3, "Got any metal in your pockets?"]]

fields.title: Gentlemen!

fields.title: Money to make
fields.dialog: [["Lawyer", "Stan"], [0, "Doors and windows are locked."], [0, "You boys have your five hundred in cash ready?"], [1, "Yeah."], [0, "Alright. Then I've got this big bowl set here, to catch all the money we are about to make."]]

fields.title: Inventing things
fields.dialog: [["Lawyer", "Spirit"], [0, "What is your name, spirit?"], [1, "Burns. Jimmy Burns. What's it to you? Who are you, mugs?"], [0, "That's how people talked in the past."], [0, "We have a claim against a John Harrington. Do you know him spirit?"], [1, "Well, maybe I do and maybe I don't."], [1, "Might need a little something something to jar my memory."], [0, "We got to grease him. Put a hundred in the box."], [1, "Oh yeah, Harrington. I know him."], [1, "Always going around inventing things."]]

fields.title: Telling you
fields.dialog: [["Cartman"], [0, "Dude, I'm telling you it was freaking hysterical."]]

fields.title: Government out
fields.dialog: [["Cartman"], [0, "Exactly how long are we going to sit around as our freedoms are stripped away one by one."], [0, "Is time for us to stand together and say, we want the government out of our bathrooms."]]

fields.dialog: [["Lawyer", "Stan", "Kyle", "Jimmy"], [0, "I'll be asking all of you to have a very open mind and a willingness to face your fears."], [0, "I warn you boys."], [0, "A suance can be very... expensive."], [1, "How expensive?"], [0, "How much do you have?"], [2, "Clyde got three thousand dollars from his mom's life insurance."], [0, "Wow!
